2. Create the EAGLE YAML config

	make config compose=base:nested:ursa >eagle.yaml

		produces: + uw config compose config/base.yaml config/nested.yaml config/ursa.yaml


3. Set the app.base value in eagle.yaml to the absolute path to the current src/ directory.
	my app.base: /scratch3/NAGAPE/epic/Wei.Huang/src/nv/EAGLE/src

4. Create training data

	make data config=eagle.yaml | tee log.data

