9. Run inference in near-real-time (NRT)

Create the EAGLE NRT config
i. make config compose=base:nested:ursa:nrt > nrt-composed.yaml


[Wei.Huang@ufe03 src]$ make config compose=base:nested:ursa:nrt > nrt-composed.yaml
+ uw config compose config/base.yaml config/nested.yaml config/ursa.yaml config/nrt.yaml


iii. Realize the EAGLE NRT config
make realize config=nrt-composed.yaml > nrt.yaml

[Wei.Huang@ufe03 src]$ make realize config=nrt-composed.yaml > nrt.yaml
+ uw config realize --input-file nrt-composed.yaml


iv. Load current initial conditions
make data config=nrt.yaml


[Wei.Huang@ufe03 src]$ make data config=nrt.yaml
